dct_description_sm: AB Stockholms Spårvägar. Alternate title: Spårvägsmuseet T-Stationen Odenplan. Legend is in Swedish, French, German, and English. Map details all bus routes in greater Stockholm. Recto: bus routes in the inner city of Stockholm. Verso: bus routes in the greater Stockholm area. 4 large and 60 small insets front and back detail all principal routes in the city. 1964
